      <Content>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="http://blog.smarx.com/posts/custom-domain-names-in-windows-azure"&gt;http://blog.smarx.com/posts/custom-domain-names-in-windows-azure&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.programgood.net/content/binary/Windows-Live-Writer/AzureDomain-Name_9362/image_2.png"&gt;&lt;img style="background-image: none; border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px" title="image" border="0" alt="image" src="http://www.programgood.net/content/binary/Windows-Live-Writer/AzureDomain-Name_9362/image_thumb.png" width="644" height="436" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;Putting in a CNAME record for davemateer.com to point to my orchard website on Azure.&lt;/p&gt;</Content>
