      <Content>&lt;p&gt;Installed using Web Platform Installer, which seems to have installed it using Web Matrix&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;After a stop, start it worked!&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.programgood.net/content/binary/Windows-Live-Writer/Orchard-CMS_F666/image_2.png"&gt;&lt;img style="background-image: none; border-right-width: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px" title="image" border="0" alt="image" src="http://www.programgood.net/content/binary/Windows-Live-Writer/Orchard-CMS_F666/image_thumb.png" width="644" height="393" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&amp;#160;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;h3&gt;Technical Initial Thoughts:&lt;/h3&gt;  &lt;ul&gt;   &lt;li&gt;[did it!]Get orchard deployed to a production server &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Get a professional website together showcasing software development, infrastructure and hardware projects done in last x years &lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;p&gt;Where to host?&amp;#160; Need .NET4 and SQL Server (or SQL CE).&amp;#160; Azure – yes &lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;ASP.NET MVC3&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;NHibernate – ORM&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;Autofac – IoC – Orchard makes heavy use of dependency injection.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;Castle Dynamic Proxy - &lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;Proxy objects can assist in building a flexible application architecture because it allows functionality to be transparently added to code without modifying it. For example, a class could be proxied to add logging or security checking without making the code aware this functionality has been added.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;For example, NHibernate, an object/relational mapper uses DynamicProxy to provide lazy loading of data without the domain model classes being aware of this functionality.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;a few questions per day on Stackoverflow. eg &lt;a href="http://stackoverflow.com/questions/9225040/how-orchard-cms-does-the-logging"&gt;http://stackoverflow.com/questions/9225040/how-orchard-cms-does-the-logging&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;h3&gt;Pluralsight Video&lt;/h3&gt;  &lt;p&gt;Free video for intro.. then pay for the rest&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="http://localhost:65422/"&gt;http://localhost:65422/&lt;/a&gt; – using webmatrix&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;TinyMCE editor&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;h3&gt;Pages and Widgets&lt;/h3&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.programgood.net/content/binary/Windows-Live-Writer/Orchard-CMS_F666/image_6.png"&gt;&lt;img style="background-image: none; border-right-width: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px" title="image" border="0" alt="image" src="http://www.programgood.net/content/binary/Windows-Live-Writer/Orchard-CMS_F666/image_thumb_2.png" width="644" height="345" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;when editing the welcome to orchard.. it is a page.&amp;#160; When editing the Third Leader Aside it is a Widget.&amp;#160; Thie is an HTML widget.. just like a page.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.programgood.net/content/binary/Windows-Live-Writer/Orchard-CMS_F666/image_8.png"&gt;&lt;img style="background-image: none; border-right-width: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px" title="image" border="0" alt="image" src="http://www.programgood.net/content/binary/Windows-Live-Writer/Orchard-CMS_F666/image_thumb_3.png" width="569" height="294" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.programgood.net/content/binary/Windows-Live-Writer/Orchard-CMS_F666/image_10.png"&gt;&lt;img style="background-image: none; border-right-width: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px" title="image" border="0" alt="image" src="http://www.programgood.net/content/binary/Windows-Live-Writer/Orchard-CMS_F666/image_thumb_4.png" width="244" height="139" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;but dont want the bullets&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;h3&gt;Edit The Stylesheet&lt;/h3&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.programgood.net/content/binary/Windows-Live-Writer/Orchard-CMS_F666/image_12.png"&gt;&lt;img style="background-image: none; border-right-width: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px" title="image" border="0" alt="image" src="http://www.programgood.net/content/binary/Windows-Live-Writer/Orchard-CMS_F666/image_thumb_5.png" width="644" height="467" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.programgood.net/content/binary/Windows-Live-Writer/Orchard-CMS_F666/image_14.png"&gt;&lt;img style="background-image: none; border-right-width: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px" title="image" border="0" alt="image" src="http://www.programgood.net/content/binary/Windows-Live-Writer/Orchard-CMS_F666/image_thumb_6.png" width="624" height="240" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;no bullets on ul!&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.programgood.net/content/binary/Windows-Live-Writer/Orchard-CMS_F666/image_16.png"&gt;&lt;img style="background-image: none; border-right-width: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px" title="image" border="0" alt="image" src="http://www.programgood.net/content/binary/Windows-Live-Writer/Orchard-CMS_F666/image_thumb_7.png" width="558" height="484" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;h3&gt;Ordering of Main Menu and Adding Items&lt;/h3&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.programgood.net/content/binary/Windows-Live-Writer/Orchard-CMS_F666/image_18.png"&gt;&lt;img style="background-image: none; border-right-width: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px" title="image" border="0" alt="image" src="http://www.programgood.net/content/binary/Windows-Live-Writer/Orchard-CMS_F666/image_thumb_8.png" width="813" height="288" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.programgood.net/content/binary/Windows-Live-Writer/Orchard-CMS_F666/image_20.png"&gt;&lt;img style="background-image: none; border-right-width: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px" title="image" border="0" alt="image" src="http://www.programgood.net/content/binary/Windows-Live-Writer/Orchard-CMS_F666/image_thumb_9.png" width="403" height="339" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;h3&gt;Building from Source / Mercurial&lt;/h3&gt;  &lt;p&gt;downloaded source (not clone the mercurial).&amp;#160; This didn’t work deploying to Azure&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="http://docs.orchardproject.net/Documentation/Deploying-Orchard-to-Windows-Azure"&gt;http://docs.orchardproject.net/Documentation/Deploying-Orchard-to-Windows-Azure&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.programgood.net/content/binary/Windows-Live-Writer/Orchard-CMS_F666/image_22.png"&gt;&lt;img style="background-image: none; border-right-width: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px" title="image" border="0" alt="image" src="http://www.programgood.net/content/binary/Windows-Live-Writer/Orchard-CMS_F666/image_thumb_10.png" width="605" height="410" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;getting from codeplex via mercurial&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.programgood.net/content/binary/Windows-Live-Writer/Orchard-CMS_F666/image_24.png"&gt;&lt;img style="background-image: none; border-right-width: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px" title="image" border="0" alt="image" src="http://www.programgood.net/content/binary/Windows-Live-Writer/Orchard-CMS_F666/image_thumb_11.png" width="521" height="484" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;Had to change Azure tools version 1.5 to 1.6 on \AzurePackage.proj and in other places (but next bits didn’t seem totally necessary): &lt;a href="http://orchard.codeplex.com/discussions/278917"&gt;http://orchard.codeplex.com/discussions/278917&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;Put in my storage connection string (for BLOB’s) into the ServiceConfiguration.cscfg in the VS solution.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;Run ClickToBuildAzurePackage.cmd&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;&amp;#160; &amp;lt;Setting name=&amp;quot;DataConnectionString&amp;quot; value=&amp;quot;DefaultEndpointsProtocol=https;AccountName=mateerstorage3;AccountKey=eYuIdHYAtX/jzkP5a67ev3ZUt1qSu0xxxxxxxxxxxxbosh419uEkJnn0Tu4jamgUiHJ1msW5K56wh7qmKVeYiVQ==&amp;quot; /&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;Upload to Azure using the manual uploader from Silverlight admin interface.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p&gt;Connection string for the database&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;pre&gt;Data Source=zx6l3oinx1.database.windows.net;Initial Catalog=orcharddb;User ID=dave;Password=xxxx;Trusted_Connection=False;Encrypt=True;MultipleActiveResultSets=True&lt;/pre&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.programgood.net/content/binary/Windows-Live-Writer/Orchard-CMS_F666/image_26.png"&gt;&lt;img style="background-image: none; border-right-width: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px" title="image" border="0" alt="image" src="http://www.programgood.net/content/binary/Windows-Live-Writer/Orchard-CMS_F666/image_thumb_12.png" width="244" height="139" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h3&gt;Downloaded Orchard.Azure Version from Codeplex&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I actually did this first to make sure connection strings were right and to prove Orchard worked on Azure.&amp;#160; However did the above after so I could have full control and deploy to an extra small instance.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;changed the dataconnectionstring to this:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;lt;ConfigurationSettings&amp;gt; 
  &lt;br /&gt;&amp;#160;&amp;#160;&amp;#160;&amp;#160;&amp;#160; &amp;lt;Setting name=&amp;quot;DataConnectionString&amp;quot; value=&amp;quot;DefaultEndpointsProtocol=https;AccountName=mateerstorage3;AccountKey=thisisasecret==&amp;quot; /&amp;gt; 

  &lt;br /&gt;&amp;#160;&amp;#160;&amp;#160;&amp;#160;&amp;#160; &amp;lt;Setting name=&amp;quot;Microsoft.WindowsAzure.Plugins.Diagnostics.ConnectionString&amp;quot; value=&amp;quot;UseDevelopmentStorage=true&amp;quot; /&amp;gt; 

  &lt;br /&gt;&amp;#160;&amp;#160;&amp;#160; &amp;lt;/ConfigurationSettings&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.programgood.net/content/binary/Windows-Live-Writer/Orchard-CMS_F666/image_28.png"&gt;&lt;img style="background-image: none; border-right-width: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; border-top-width: 0px; border-bottom-width: 0px; border-left-width: 0px; padding-top: 0px" title="image" border="0" alt="image" src="http://www.programgood.net/content/binary/Windows-Live-Writer/Orchard-CMS_F666/image_thumb_13.png" width="644" height="221" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;should be mateerstorage3'&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;put in this in the connection settings:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Server=tcp:zx6l3oinx1.database.windows.net,1433;Database=orcharddb;User &lt;a href="mailto:ID=dave@zx6l3oinx1;Password=myPassword;Trusted_Connection=False;Encrypt=True"&gt;ID=dave@zx6l3oinx1;Password=myPassword;Trusted_Connection=False;Encrypt=True&lt;/a&gt;;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.programgood.net/content/binary/Windows-Live-Writer/Orchard-CMS_F666/image_30.png"&gt;&lt;img style="background-image: none; border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: inline; border-top: 0px; border-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px" title="image" border="0" alt="image" src="http://www.programgood.net/content/binary/Windows-Live-Writer/Orchard-CMS_F666/image_thumb_14.png" width="244" height="203" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</Content>
